T* (POST /api/handoff/generate      routes.ts:1044 Ś handoff note generation) Tj
T* (GET  /api/audit-log             routes.ts:560  Ś has isCPO\(\) check inside, but no middleware) Tj
T* (GET  /api/audit-log/export      routes.ts:576  Ś same pattern: isCPO\(\) check inside handler only) Tj
