10.3499999999999996 TL
0.059 0.09 0.165 rg
48. 608. Td
(The scheduling routes call getSiteAccess\(\) which internally reads req.session.user and returns an error object if not found Ś) Tj
T* (functionally equivalent to an auth check but not enforced at the middleware level. The /api/generate-note and) Tj
T* (/api/handoff/generate routes require independent verification of whether they enforce auth.) Tj
